<A>__{when drayton reaches the two steps of the altar, he beckons the organist to him. she comes, and he whispers something to her. he then motions his wife nearer to him, and also whispers something to her. mrs. drayton goes off through a side door by the altar, while the organist makes her way down the aisle through the congregation to stand by the door.}
